criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of definite MS according to Poser criteria;

          -  Attention impairment defined as abnormal PASAT score;

          -  Written and signed informed consent;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy or lactation;

          -  Steroid treatment;

          -  Persistent psychostimulant treatment;

          -  MS relapse;
